I had booked 2 nights at this hotel via booking.com, however could not make it to Venice on time due to Italian transportation strike, I informed booking.com about my predicament and rightfuly so changed my booking to only 1 night.	As a courtesy I informed the hotel about the change and was told insistingly that I will have to pay the full 2 nights which I believe was unfair so I cancelled my booking altogether via booking.com.